    "description": "<strong>致失去深爱之人的你</strong><br><br>尽管已无法再见，但你却无论如何都还想再与对方见一面，再相拥一次。你深爱的人如今身在何处？真的不能再相见了吗？<br>在In His Time这款2D解谜冒险游戏中，你的这些疑问将会得到真挚的回答。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/845b340b94bce0e2ae706948394ed8e9.poster.avif?t=1748676355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/845b340b94bce0e2ae706948394ed8e9.webm?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/845b340b94bce0e2ae706948394ed8e9.mp4?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏的主角少年奥利，父亲早年去世，只剩下他与母亲莱拉两人相依为命。但是最近由于母亲生病，奥利不得不在上学的同时还要兼顾家务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/7c4462397590e970bd6e255a3522d80f.poster.avif?t=1748676355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/7c4462397590e970bd6e255a3522d80f.webm?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/7c4462397590e970bd6e255a3522d80f.mp4?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/3934d90e5c893c017493bdb419693700.poster.avif?t=1748676355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/3934d90e5c893c017493bdb419693700.webm?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/3934d90e5c893c017493bdb419693700.mp4?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>同时在学校，奥利不仅受到了孩子王鲍比和被牵扯进来的米拉、休格的霸凌，还要面对老师的责骂……少年奥利每天都承受着来自这个世界的压迫。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/e3c1176a8c53e48418c51b4091fd6273.poster.avif?t=1748676355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/e3c1176a8c53e48418c51b4091fd6273.webm?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/e3c1176a8c53e48418c51b4091fd6273.mp4?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有一天奥利在鲍比的胁迫下，一起偷偷溜进了一栋阴森的房子。在他们偷走了某件作品的“零件”后逃跑时，奥利因为慢了一步而被房子的主人约瑟夫抓住。<br>约瑟夫是一名钟表匠，他在向奥利了解基本情况后承诺只要能把“零件”取回来，就不会再向他们追究。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/dfe6ded3a2de1bbbcd223dfa4bc20652.poster.avif?t=1748676355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/dfe6ded3a2de1bbbcd223dfa4bc20652.webm?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/dfe6ded3a2de1bbbcd223dfa4bc20652.mp4?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>奥利最终能够与鲍比他们互相谅解吗？母亲的病情会如何？而约瑟夫又是何人？<br>少年奥利的冒险旅程就此展开。请一同来见证故事的结局以及奥利的成长吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/c6d9751b132a4e4dd7329a8b789e5346.poster.avif?t=1748676355\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/c6d9751b132a4e4dd7329a8b789e5346.webm?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/c6d9751b132a4e4dd7329a8b789e5346.mp4?t=1748676355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>人物介绍</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2361610/extras/57b82e47dfba23d02a2f310621a7ae1f.avif?t=1748676355\" width=640 height=360 /></span>",
